info.author: Paul Sokolovsky
info.description:
This is a module ported from CPython standard library to be compatible with
Pycopy project (https://github.com/pfalcon/pycopy). Usually, this means that
small patches were applied for features not supported (yet, or at all) in
Pycopy. Sometimes, heavier changes might have been done. Note that CPython
modules are written with availability of vast resources in mind, and may not
work for Pycopy ports with limited heap memory (RAM). If you are affected by
such a case, please help reimplement the module in minimalistic way from
scratch.
info.name: pycopy-stat
info.summary: CPython stat module ported to Pycopy
